WEBVTT

00:15.000 --> 00:17.951
At the left we can see...

00:18.166 --> 00:20.083
At the right we can see the...

00:20.119 --> 00:21.962
...the head-snarlers

00:21.999 --> 00:24.368
Everything is safe.
Perfectly safe.

00:24.582 --> 00:27.035
Emo?

00:28.206 --> 00:29.996
Watch out!

00:47.037 --> 00:48.494
Are you hurt?

00:51.994 --> 00:53.949
I don't think so.
You?

00:55.160 --> 00:56.985
I'm Ok.

00:57.118 --> 01:01.111
Get up.
Emo. it's not safe here.

01:02.034 --> 01:03.573
Let's go.

01:03.610 --> 01:05.114
What's next?

01:05.200 --> 01:09.146
You'll see!

01:16.032 --> 01:18.022
Emo.
This way.

01:34.237 --> 01:35.481
Follow me!

02:11.106 --> 02:12.480
Hurry Emo!

02:48.059 --> 02:49.930
You're not paying attention!

02:50.142 --> 02:54.052
I just want to answer the...
...phone.

02:54.974 --> 02:57.972
Emo. look.
I mean listen.

02:59.140 --> 03:02.008
You have to learn to listen.

03:03.140 --> 03:04.965
This is not some game.

03:05.056 --> 03:09.345
You. I mean we.
we could easily die out here.

03:10.014 --> 03:13.959
Listen.
listen to the sounds of the machine.

03:18.054 --> 03:20.009
Listen to your breathing.

04:27.001 --> 04:28.956
Well. don't you ever get tired of this?

04:29.084 --> 04:30.909
Tired?!?

04:31.126 --> 04:34.491
Emo. the machine is like clockwork.

04:35.083 --> 04:37.074
One move out of place...

04:37.166 --> 04:39.121
...and you're ground to a pulp.

04:40.958 --> 04:42.004
But isn't it -

04:42.041 --> 04:46.034
Pulp. Emo!
Is that what you want. pulp?

04:47.040 --> 04:48.995
Emo. your goal in life...

04:50.081 --> 04:51.953
...pulp?

05:41.156 --> 05:43.028
Emo. close your eyes.

05:44.156 --> 05:46.027
Why?
- Now!

05:51.155 --> 05:52.102
Ok.

05:53.113 --> 05:54.688
Good.

05:59.070 --> 06:02.103
What do you see at your left side. Emo?

06:04.028 --> 06:05.899
Nothing.
- Really?

06:06.027 --> 06:07.105
No. nothing at all.

06:07.944 --> 06:11.984
And at your right.
what do you see at your right side. Emo?

06:13.151 --> 06:16.102
The same Proog. exactly the same...

06:16.942 --> 06:19.098
...nothing!
- Great.

06:40.105 --> 06:42.724
Listen Proog! Do you hear that!

06:43.105 --> 06:44.894
Can we go here?

06:44.979 --> 06:47.894
There?
It isn't safe. Emo.

06:49.145 --> 06:52.013
But...
- Trust me. it's not.

06:53.020 --> 06:54.145
Maybe I could...

06:54.181 --> 06:55.969
No.

06:57.102 --> 06:59.934
NO!

07:00.144 --> 07:03.058
Any further questions. Emo?

07:03.976 --> 07:05.090
No.

07:09.059 --> 07:10.089
Emo?

07:11.142 --> 07:13.058
Emo. why...

07:13.095 --> 07:14.022
Emo...

07:14.058 --> 07:18.003
...why can't you see
the beauty of this place?

07:18.141 --> 07:20.048
The way it works.

07:20.140 --> 07:23.895
How perfect it is.

07:23.932 --> 07:26.964
No. Proog. I don't see.

07:27.056 --> 07:29.970
I don't see because there's nothing there.

07:31.055 --> 07:34.965
And why should I trust my
life to something that isn't there?

07:35.055 --> 07:36.926
Well can you tell me that?

07:37.054 --> 07:38.926
Answer me!

07:42.970 --> 07:44.000
Proog...

07:45.053 --> 07:46.985
...you're a sick man!

07:47.022 --> 07:48.918
Stay away from me!

07:52.052 --> 07:54.884
No! Emo! It's a trap!

07:55.135 --> 07:56.931
Hah. it's a trap.

07:56.968 --> 08:01.043
At the left side you can see
the hanging gardens of Babylon!

08:01.967 --> 08:03.957
How's that for a trap?

08:05.050 --> 08:06.922
No. Emo.

08:09.008 --> 08:12.088
At the right side you can see...
...well guess what...

08:12.924 --> 08:14.665
...the colossus of Rhodes!

08:15.132 --> 08:16.053
No!

08:16.090 --> 08:21.919
The colossus of Rhodes
and it is here just for you Proog.

08:51.001 --> 08:52.923
It is there...

08:52.959 --> 08:56.040
I'm telling you.
Emo...

08:57.000 --> 08:59.867
...it is.
